### this is an example file of how the .env file is configured, 
### and currently it holds the following fields.
### When you create your own .env file, make sure to replace the placeholder 
### values with your actual configuration values.


## MySQL Database Configuration
DB_URL=jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/quickparkdb
DB_USERNAME=root
DB_PASSWORD=your-mysql-password-here

## JWT Configuration
JWT_SECRET=your-jwt-secret-key-here-minimum-256-bits
JWT_EXPIRATION=86400000

## Admin Secret Key
ADMIN_SECRET_KEY=your-admin-secret-key-here

## Email Configuration
## For Gmail: You MUST use an App Password, not your regular password
## How to get Gmail App Password:
## 1. Enable 2-Factor Authentication on your Google Account
## 2. Go to https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
## 3. Select "Mail" and generate a password
## 4. Use that 16-character password below
MAIL_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
MAIL_PORT=587
MAIL_USERNAME=your-email@gmail.com
MAIL_PASSWORD=your-16-character-app-password-here
EMAIL_FROM_NAME=QuickPark Support